        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "GIFTS UNDER $300",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For those looking to splurge a little, consider high-performance golf shoes that offer both comfort and style on the course, making them a perfect gift for the avid golfer. Another excellent choice is a sleek and stylish jacket, versatile enough for early morning rounds or a casual day out. A timeless sweater also makes a wonderful gift, providing both warmth and an iconic, classic look that any dad would appreciate.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["heading_1", "text_1"],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
