          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "GIFTS UNDER $200",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If your budget is slightly lower, you can’t go wrong with performance polos. These high-quality, breathable shirts are ideal for a day on the course or a casual outing. Luxurious knits are another great option, offering comfort and style that are perfect for layering. For the golfing dad, a stylish golf bag that combines functionality with fashion would make an impressive gift.</p>"
