          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For those seeking budget-friendly options, stylish hats are a practical and fashionable choice, perfect for keeping dad looking sharp on and off the course. Premium golf gloves, known for their excellent grip and comfort, are sure to be appreciated. Additionally, comfortable socks that provide durability and style make for a thoughtful and practical gift that dad can use every day.</p>"
