          "settings": {
            "text": "POLO PICKS FOR DAD",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When it comes to polo shirts, a classic performance polo combines timeless style with modern performance, making it a must-have for any dad. A sleek stripe polo, featuring a stylish design and premium fabric, is perfect for the fashionable dad who likes to make a statement. Another excellent choice is a comfortable golf polo, known for its quality and comfort, which is a great addition to any golf wardrobe.</p>"
